Vedas API is an integrated database open API which enables to access Ancient Indian Vedas by their addresses
This API provides us with the hindi translation as well as the original shukta or shlokas
To get started with this api, you have to input given parameters to access the data
bookname/bookid = The Book name from which the data should be collected, example - Mahabharat, RigVeda, ect
chapterID = The Chapter in which the shloka must be found
Sukta/Partition = The Partition you finally want to access


